<!-- Types of systems -->
<section class="en-section">
  <div class="en-container">
    <h2>Types of Glass Curtain Systems</h2>
    <p>Glass curtain systems are not all built the same. Over the years, the market has evolved from basic sliding panel systems to sophisticated frameless configurations with motorised opening options. Understanding the differences helps you choose the right system for your property and budget.</p>

    <table class="compare-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>System Type</th>
          <th>Best For</th>
          <th>Opening Style</th>
